        References
        <div>
            <p>
                <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/virtual-machines/extensions/dsc-overview" target="_blank" rel="noopener" >Introduction to the Azure Desired State Configuration extension handler</a>            
            </p>
            <p>
                <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/powershell/dsc/azuredsc" target="_blank" rel="noopener" >Using DSC on Microsoft Azure</a>            
            </p>
            <p>
                <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/automation/automation-dsc-overview" target="_blank" rel="noopener" >Azure Automation State Configuration Overview</a>
            </p>
            <p>
                <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/automation/automation-quickstart-dsc-configuration" target="_blank" rel="noopener" >Configure a Linux virtual machine with Desired State Configuration</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </li>
</ul>